{Speech 10}{}{What do I know about him? He came to Broken Hills out of the desert. He had nothing but his own hands and head. He looked like someone was hunting him, but he wouldn't say who. In general he always kept quiet about his past. And... he's just a magnificent caravan master. That's all.}
{Speech 10 Answer 8}{}{I have more questions.}
{Speech 10 Answer Exit}{}{Thanks.}
{Speech 11}{}{My apologies, but I don't have any work for you yet.}
