{Speech 13}{}{You did a great job with your task, @sex@|mister|miss|! How about you work for us some more?}
{Speech 13 Answer Exit}{}{I'll think about it.@@Anything's possible.@@Thanks.}
{Speech 14}{}{Ah, yes. @arg leader@ told me about this problem. You'll have to pay so we can forget about this unfortunate misunderstanding. The fee will be @arg money@ coins.}
